{"file":"\u003c!DOCTYPE html\u003e\r\n\u003chtml lang=\"en\"\u003e\r\n\u003chead\u003e\r\n\u003cmeta charset=\"UTF-8\"\u003e\r\n\u003c!--[if IE]\u003e\u003cmeta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\"\u003e\u003c![endif]--\u003e\r\n\u003cmeta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\"\u003e\r\n\u003cmeta name=\"generator\" content=\"Asciidoctor 1.5.5\"\u003e\r\n\u003ctitle\u003eOpioids\u003c/title\u003e\r\n\u003clink rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:300,300italic,400,400italic,600,600italic%7CNoto+Serif:400,400italic,700,700italic%7CDroid+Sans+Mono:400,700\"\u003e\r\n\u003clink rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"./asciidoctor.css\"\u003e\r\n\u003c/head\u003e\r\n\u003cbody class=\"article\"\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv id=\"content\"\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv class=\"sect1\"\u003e\r\n\u003ch2 id=\"_opioids\"\u003eOpioids\u003c/h2\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv class=\"sectionbody\"\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv class=\"sect2\"\u003e\r\n\u003ch3 id=\"_guidelines\"\u003eGuidelines\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv class=\"olist arabic\"\u003e\r\n\u003col class=\"arabic\"\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003eEnsure morphine/oxycodone order is for immediate release\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003eMorphine and hydromorphone are NOT dosed the same\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003eMonitor RR and SpO2 during and after IV bolus.\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003eUse cautiously with CNS depressants like benzos and anti-histamines\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003eAlways reduce calculated dose by 25-50% to account for incomplete cross-tolerance.\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ol\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv class=\"sect2\"\u003e\r\n\u003ch3 id=\"_equivalency\"\u003eEquivalency\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv class=\"paragraph\"\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e1 mg PO oxycodone = 1.3 mg IV morphine = 0.2 IV hydromorphone\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv class=\"sect2\"\u003e\r\n\u003ch3 id=\"_contraindications\"\u003eContraindications\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv class=\"olist arabic\"\u003e\r\n\u003col class=\"arabic\"\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003eHypersensitivity to morphine sulfate or any component\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003eSevere respiratory depression in a setting without resuscitative equipment or appropriate monitoring.\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003eAcute or severe asthma\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003eUse caution in patients with hypercarbia or paralytic ileus.\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ol\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv class=\"sect2\"\u003e\r\n\u003ch3 id=\"_routes_of_administration\"\u003eRoutes of Administration\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv class=\"ulist\"\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003eIV - Morphine, Hydromorphone\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003ePO = Morphine, Oxycodone\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv class=\"paragraph\"\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"http://www.crlonline.com/lco/action/doc/retrieve/docid/pdh_f/2853079\"\u003eMorphine (Lexicomp)\u003c/a\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003ca href=\"http://www.crlonline.com/lco/action/doc/retrieve/docid/pdh_f/129887\"\u003eHydromorphone (Lexicomp)\u003c/a\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003ca href=\"http://www.crlonline.com/lco/action/doc/retrieve/docid/pdh_f/129937\"\u003eOxycodone (Lexicomp)\u003c/a\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003ca href=\"hybrid://home\"\u003ePainApp Home\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cscript\u003e\r\n    document.querySelector(\"body.article\").addEventListener(\"click\", doSomething, false);\r\n    \r\n    function doSomething(e) {\r\n        var clickedItem = e.target.href;\r\n        window.postMessage(clickedItem);\r\n        e.preventDefault();\r\n        return false;\r\n    }\r\n\u003c/script\u003e\r\n\u003c/body\u003e\r\n\u003c/html\u003e"}
